Cell - Class in model
Represents a cell in the minesweeper board
Cell(int, int) - Constructor for class model.Cell
Constructs a new cell object with default values (unflagged, no mine, uncovered) and sets its location accordingly given the specified parameters
CellDisplay - Class in view
Represents the visual representation of the cell in the Minesweeper simulation.
CellDisplay(Cell, int, int) - Constructor for class view.CellDisplay
Constructs a new cell on the screen with default parameters (green, uncovered)
